{"tid":481673,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"港元1個月拆息飆至0.92厘　H按升至封頂位","createTime":"2017-11-27T11:54:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-01T05:52:56.000Z","uid":56690,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"476851fd5707a0b8a82d04db958fca2a3b5cceac","tid":481673,"uid":56690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T11:54:35.000Z","msg":"香港銀行同業拆息(Hibor)中，隔夜息報0.63304厘，1星期報0.84036厘，1個月則報0.92250厘。當中1個月拆息升至2008年金融海嘯年12月11日以來的高位，選擇H按(拆息)計劃的按揭人士，按揭利率將升至2.15%封頂位。 <br />\n<br />\n目前H按計劃分為1個月拆息加1.28厘，或1個月拆息加1.3厘，即實際按息理論上約2.2厘或2.22厘，由於H按計劃設有以最優惠利率(P)(P現為5.25厘)減3.1%為利率封頂位的安排，換言之按揭人士的按息將上調至2.15厘。 <br />\n<br />\n1個拆息已由今年十月初時0.5972厘不斷上升，當時H按實際按息僅約1.9厘。而金融海嘯年12月11日的1個月拆息為1.04厘，及後不斷尋底。"},{"pid":"5a8f4db62bc218ff80be65e732eeeeb9a4be1297","tid":481673,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T11:55:34.000Z","msg":"即係點"},{"pid":"c67bb604324c538cb75d8f8fe7e5a73375b54367","tid":481673,"uid":8257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T11:56:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>即係點</blockquote><br />\n加息"},{"pid":"6f622c701305c5d2fb43451c77be2193b2541f63","tid":481673,"uid":30604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T11:57:37.000Z","msg":"股 J O Y I S C O M I N G"},{"pid":"b2b28160f6b162ab3b8b152f78cc990057826659","tid":481673,"uid":77717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T11:58:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>即係點</blockquote><br />\n加息</blockquote><br />\n樓市仆街未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6164fdd7a87a0bc7acc4141b9fb89ee47f30416","tid":481673,"uid":5278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T11:59:50.000Z","msg":"流動性出出地事"},{"pid":"18c2b5d9790b92eade11647d2a074eb597e1191e","tid":481673,"uid":89220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T12:03:03.000Z","msg":"係咪即係個個都攬住舊現金搞到市場流動現金不足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgm